quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Na ha se Rona ba atollotseng sefuba sa hau
  94,2,Ra u imulla moroalo
  94,3,O neng o u roba mokokotlo
  94,4,Le hona ho tumisa boemo ba hau
  94,5,Ruri! Ho teng topollo mathateng ohle
  94,6,Ruri! Mathateng oohle ho teng topollo
  94,7,"Kahoo, ha u lopolotsoe, tsitlellela ho sebetsa ka thata"
  94,8,U retellehele ho Mong`a hau
  95,1,Ka Feikha le Olive
  95,2,Le ka Thaba ea Sinai
  95,3,Le ka motse o ts’ireletsong
  95,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka tlholeho e babatsehang
  95,5,Eaba Re mo kokobetsa ka boemo bo tlase-tlase
  95,6,"Ntle le feela ea kholoang a etsa liketso tse lokileng, bao moputso oa bona o ke ke oa sitoa"
  95,7,Ke eng joale se ka o emang pele malebana le kahlolo
  95,8,Na ha se Allah Moahloli Ea Seli
  96,1,Bala! Ka lebitso la Mong`a hau Ea hlotseng
  96,2,Ea hlotseng motho ka lehloele la mali
  96,3,Bala! Mong`a hau U lereko le fetisisang
  96,4,Ea rutang ho ngola ka pene
  96,5,O rutile motho seo a sa se tsebeng
  96,6,Che! Empa motho o tlola meeli
  96,7,Ka ho nahana hore ke maikhona
  96,8,Ruri! Poelo ea tsohle e ho Mong`a hau
  96,9,Na o kile oa bona ea sitisang
  96,10,Lekhabunyane nakong eo le rapelang
  96,11,Na u kile oa bona ebang o its’etlehile tataisong
  96,12,Kapa o khothaletsa hoba mosa
  96,13,"Na o kile oa bona ebang u latola tataiso `nete, o oa furalla"
  96,14,Na ha a elelloe hore Allah U’a bona
  96,15,"Ha a hlokomele! ha a sa khaotse, re tla mo tutla ka qoba ea moriri –"
  96,16,"O leshano, o bile o silafetse –"
  96,17,"Joale, ha a bitse bathusi ba hae"
  96,18,Re tla bitsa manyeloi a kahlolo
  96,19,Se ka mo natsa. Empa u ithapalatse le hona ho ba haufinyane le Allah
  97,1,Ruri! Qura’n Re e senotse ka bosiu ba matla
  97,2,Ke eng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na bosiu ba matla ke eng
  97,3,Bosiu ba matla bo molemo ho feta likhoeli tse sekete
  97,4,Ke nako eo manyeloi le Khabariele ba theohelang lefats’eng ka tumello ea Mong`a bona le ka melao eohle
  97,5,Khotso!... Sena Ho fihlela chabo ea letsatsi
  98,1,"Haele ba latolang har’a Batho ba Lengolo le har`a ba hedene, ba ne ba ke ke ba sokoloha ho fihlela sesupo se hlakileng se finyeletse ho bona"
  98,2,"Sa moromuoa ea tsoang ho Allah, ea balang maqephe a hloekileng"
  98,3,"A jereng melao e nepahetseng, e topileng"
  98,4,Batho ba Lengolo ba ne ba ke ke ba arohana ho fihlela kamor’a hoba sesupo se hlakileng se finyelle ho bona
  98,5,"Ba ne ba laetsoe ho sebeletsa Allah le ho boloka tumelo ea bona e hloekile malebana le Eena, e be batho ba topileng ka tlholeho le hona ho phethahatsa lithapelo le ho fana ka linyehelo. Seo ke tumelo ea ‘nete"
  98,6,"Haele ba latolang har’a batho ba Lengolo le har`a bahedene, ba tla eba mollong-oa-lihele ho phela teng. Ke libopuoa tse nyonts’ang"
  98,7,"Bohle ba-kholoang, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, – bona ke libopuoa tse molemo"
  98,8,"Moputso oa bona o ho Allah: lirapa tsa Edene, tseo linoka li phallang tlas’a tsona, ba tla phela teng kahosafeleng. Allah U tla nyakalla ke bona le bona ba tla nyakalla ke Eena. Tsena li molemong oa ba ts’abang Mong`a bona"
  99,1,Ha lefats’e le sisingoa la mathetho
  99,2,Le itlhohlolla moroalo
  99,3,"Motho o tla re: “Molato ke eng ka lefats’e”"
  99,4,Ke mohla lefat’se le tla bolela nalane ea lona
  99,5,Hobane Mong`a hau U tla le susumetsa
  99,6,Mohlang oo batho ba tla nyolosa ba theosa ka mekhahlelo ho ea bonts’oa liketso tsa bona
  99,7,Mong le mong ea etsang ketso e lokileng e fokolang sa ntoana- la-botsikoane o tla e bona
  99,8,Mong le mong ea etsang sebe le ha se ka fokola sa ntoana-la- botsikoane o tla se bona
  100,1,"Ka lipitsi tse mathang, tse hemeselang"
  100,2,Tseo maotong a tsona ho qobang litlhase
  100,3,Tse tsometsang tlhaselo ka matjeke
  100,4,E be li tsosa leroele khabong
  100,5,Li parola lebotho la lira ka lehare e le ngatana ng’oe
  100,6,Ruri! Motho o hloka teboho ho Mong`a hae
  100,7,E bile ke paki holim’a seo
  100,8,O lehala leratong la leruo